    dc:description "FIGURE 14. A–D. Aulacofusus canaliculatus n. sp. A. Holotype, LACM 3667, SE of Agattu Island, 135 m, 66.6 mm; B. Paratype, RNC 4143, S of Buldir Island, 71 m, 53.3 mm; C. Aulacofusus periscelidus (Dall, 1891), RNC 4860, W of Hawadax (Rat) Island, 94 m, 77.47 mm; D. RNC 4625, Adak Island, 18 m, 69.1 mm; E–G. Aulacofusus tanagaensis n. sp.; E. Holotype, LACM 3665, W of Tanaga Island, 53 m, 54.9 mm; F. Paratype, RNC 4585, W of Tanaga Island, 95 m, 54.0 mm; G. Radula, paratype, bar = 200 µm." ;
